metadata.name: Zelensky # 1.  Donate To Ukraine’s Military
metadata.description:
Ukraine's defenders are brave warriors that are fighting heroically to stop Russia’s invasion of Ukraine. They protect our land, they protect Europe, they protect freedom itself.

Donate to Ukraine's Military (https://bit.ly/army-donation-ukraine) or purchase this one-of-a-kind Zelensky art. Help us protect freedom.

The purchase of this item will convert into 3 personal protective equipment kits (bulletproof vest + helmet) for Ukrainians at the frontline. Any extra money raised will go to buy more kits and radios. 

Shields volunteers in Ukraine will ensure fast delivery of the kits directly to defenders who need it the most.
